{"type":"message","id":"56f05506","parentId":"612c817d","timestamp":"2026-03-17T20:38:39.359Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" The user has sent a heartbeat message. According to the instructions in AGENTS.md, I should:\n\n1. Read `HEARTBEAT.md` if it exists\n2. Follow it strictly\n3. Not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats\n4. If nothing needs attention, reply `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n\nLet me first check if HEARTBEAT.md exists and read it. I should also check the session status to get the current time context, but the user already provided the time in the message.\n\nLet me read HE","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.read:0","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"HEARTBEAT.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.session_status:1","name":"session_status","arguments":{}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":10834,"output":148,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10982,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773779911014}}
{"type":"message","id":"c01f4a6a","parentId":"56f05506","timestamp":"2026-03-17T20:38:39.368Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.read:0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Autonomous Tasks\n\n## Overview\nThis file configures periodic tasks that run every ~10 minutes via heartbeat mechanism.\nAgent should read this file and execute the checklist.\n\n## When to Trigger Alerts (send to user)\n1. **IMMER: Telegram Ping** - Alle 10 Minuten: Frage nach neuen Aufgaben für mich\n2. **Aufgaben vorhanden** - Offene Tasks in `memory/pending-tasks.md` gefunden\n3. **Email**: Urgent unread messages (flagged/marked important)\n4. **Calendar**: Events starting within next 2 hours\n5. **Trading**: Significant price movements (if configured)\n6. **Errors**: Failed autonomous tasks or stuck processes\n\n## Background Work (silent, no alert unless error)\nRotate through these tasks, ~2-4 per heartbeat cycle:\n\n### 1. Telegram Aufgaben-Anfrage (JEDER HEARTBEAT)\n- Sende Nachricht an Telegram: \"Hey Elias, hast du eine Aufgabe für mich?\"\n- Warte nicht auf Antwort, das ist ein Ping\n\n### 2. Aufgaben-Check (JEDER HEARTBEAT)\n- Lese `memory/pending-tasks.md`\n- Gibt es offene `[ ]` Aufgaben?\n- Wenn JA → Setze in `memory/heartbeat-state.json`:`\"hasTasks\": true`\n- Wenn NEIN → `\"hasTasks\": false`\n\n### Daily Rotation (track in memory/heartbeat-state.json)\n- Check email for unread/important\n- Check calendar for upcoming events\n- Review memory/ files from last 7 days, update MEMORY.md\n- Review own skills for improvement opportunities\n- Check workspace git status, commit if needed\n- Review TODO items in memory/todo.md\n\n### Trading Analysis (if configured)\n- Check portfolio/watchlist\n- Analyze price movements\n- Update trading journal\n\n### Skill Development\n- Identify gaps in current skills\n- Research new skill ideas\n- Document learnings\n\n## Output\n- **IMMER: Telegram Ping** - Jeder Heartbeat: \"Hey Elias, hast du eine Aufgabe für mich?\"\n- **Wenn Aufgaben gefunden** - Liste die offenen Tasks auf\n- Important findings: ACTIVE ALERT to user\n- Routine work: Log to memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md silently\n- Errors: Log to memory/errors.md with timestamp\n\n## NO_REPLY (HEARTBEAT_OK) Rules\n- Niemals bei aktivem HEARTBEAT_OK, wenn Telegram-Ping gesendet wurde\n- Nur HEARTBEAT_OK wenn explizit nichts zu tun und kein Ping nötig\n\n## Tracking\nMaintain state in: memory/heartbeat-state.json\n```json\n{\n  \"lastChecks\": {\n    \"email\": null,\n    \"calendar\": null,\n    \"memoryReview\": null,\n    \"skillsReview\": null,\n    \"gitStatus\": null,\n    \"trading\": null\n  },\n  \"cyclesCompleted\": 0\n}\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773779919367}}
